Grid FlexBox: Header,aside,footer,RightMenu,main.

flex: It is one dimensional/directional
grid: It is two dimensional/directional

To use:
flex: display:flex;
grid: display:grid;

flex: It is easy and flexible to work
Grid:It is complex but very powerful

flex: it has limited tools
grid: advanced tools

display:grid;  -- it defines the grid container
grid-template-rows: it specifies how many rows in a webpage has been divided and
                    how much each row has occupied

grid-template-column: it specifies how many couls in a webpage and 
                      how much each column was divided/occupied.

grid-row: it specifies the start and end of each row
grid-column: it specifies the start and end of each column.
